title: A quick thank you!
body:
Just a quick thank you to all of our followers and supporters <3

We have only been ARMY for around 6 months but have felt such love and support from everyone and we now have over 200 followers!

Both admins have had an insane 6 months - having been lucky enough to have seen BTS in London in October and yesterday seeing Burn the Stage at the Cinema in Sheffield. (The movie was amazing and we feel so insfired having seen it. BTS are truly the softest, most lovely human beings alive <3)



We have plenty of BTS scenarios, fics and lists to come. Just a sneak peak of what we have planned soon:

* A super hot “straight” threesome fic including 2 of the members (we have already written a Jimin/V/OC fic here )

* More fics from the Suga universe with his girlfriend, Jeong-sun from our headcanon universe

* Your first time having sex with each member (Suga’s and Jin’s have already been written and can be found here (S) and here (J)

* Jungkook’s first date with an older woman (eventually headcanon universe)

* Trying anal with each member

* Most likely to least likely to cheat

* How they say I love you for the first time


and loads loads more (both admins have dozens of unwritten scenarios we are slowly trying to work through)

Once again, thanks for the love and support ARMY <3

Our full mastertlist can be found here 

to keep you entertained and insfired until our next fic :) <3
